==English==
===Etymology===
From Dr. [[w:Pangloss|Pangloss]], a character in [[w:Voltaire|Voltaire]]'s ''[[w:Candide|Candide]]''
===Adjective===
'''Panglossian'''
# Naively or unreasonably [[optimistic]].
:* ''Though he took a '''Panglossian''' view of the world in his youth, he became jaded as he grew older.
# of relating to the view that this is the best of all possible worlds.